        <span class="meta-tag">Free Tier: Unlimited</span>
        <span class="meta-tag">Auth: None</span>
        <span class="meta-tag">Rate Score: 10/10</span>
      </div>
      <p>The simplest image API ever created. Just construct a URL with your desired dimensions and you get a random high-quality photo. No API key, no SDK, no nothing. Perfect for mockups and prototypes.</p>
      
      <div class="card"><h4>Key Strengths:</h4><ul><li>No API key needed</li><li>URL-based — no fetch required</li><li>Custom dimensions via URL</li><li>Blur and grayscale effects</li></ul></div>
      
    <details class="code-block">
      <summary>View Code Example</summary>
      <div class="code-wrapper">
        <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
        <pre><code>// Just use these URLs directly in <img> tags:
// Random: https://picsum.photos/400/300
// Specific: https://picsum.photos/id/237/400/300
// Grayscale: https://picsum.photos/400/300?grayscale
// Blur: https://picsum.photos/400/300?blur=2

const res = await fetch("https://picsum.photos/id/237/info");
const info = await res.json();
console.log(`Author: $&#123;info.author&#125;, Size: $&#123;info.width&#125;x$&#123;info.height&#125;`);</code></pre>
      </div>
    </details>
      <p class="api-link"><a href="https://picsum.photos/" target="_blank">Official Documentation →</a></p>
