        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Unsplash has the highest quality photos, but Pexels offers more generous rate limits (200/hr vs 50/hr) and includes free video content. Both are free for commercial use.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Is there a free image API with no API key? <span class="faq-icon">▼</span></button>
