        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Cloudinary is the best choice for production — it handles upload, transformation, optimization, and CDN delivery. The free tier (25 credits/month) covers small to medium applications.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">Can I use Unsplash photos commercially for free? <span class="faq-icon">▼</span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes, all Unsplash photos are free for commercial and personal use under the Unsplash License. Attribution is appreciated but not required.</p></div>
